1 impr isonment. Any person convicted of a second or subsequent
2 violation shall, upon conviction, be punished by imprisonment in the
3 custody of the Department of Corrections for not less than ten (10)
4 years and not more than thirty (30) years, or by a fine of not less
5 than Twenty Thousand Dollars ($20,000.00), or by both such fine and
6 imprisonment. The violator, upon conviction, shall be required to
7 register as a sex offender under the Sex Offenders Registration Act.
8 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
